node.text:
Here is a timelapse of the castle  PearlescentMoon and I made for Minecraft RTX, using the new GeForce RTX 30-series laptop. Did you see the tutorial on how to make mega builds on my channel? If not, check it out! What do you think of this build?

Thanks to Nvidia for sponsoring the mega build tutorial, it wouldn't have been possible without them! 

#ad #NVIDIA #UltimatePlay
